SELECT [c1].[CarreraId], [c1].[Departamento], [c1].[DuracionPeriodos], [c1].[NombreCarrera], [c1].[TotalCreditos], [s].[CarreraId], [s].[CodigoMateria], [s].[EstudianteId], [s].[CodigoMateria0], [s].[AreaAcademica], [s].[AulaCodigoAula], [s].[CreditosMateria], [s].[NombreMateria], [s].[TipoMateria]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarreraId], [c].[Departamento], [c].[DuracionPeriodos], [c].[NombreCarrera], [c].[TotalCreditos]
    FROM [Carreras] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CarreraId] = @__carreraId_0
) AS [c1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[CarreraId], [c0].[CodigoMateria], [c0].[EstudianteId], [m].[CodigoMateria] AS [CodigoMateria0], [m].[AreaAcademica], [m].[AulaCodigoAula], [m].[CreditosMateria], [m].[NombreMateria], [m].[TipoMateria]
    FROM [CarreraMaterias] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Materias] AS [m] ON [c0].[CodigoMateria] = [m].[CodigoMateria]
) AS [s] ON [c1].[CarreraId] = [s].[CarreraId]
ORDER BY [c1].[CarreraId], [s].[CarreraId], [s].[CodigoMateria]
